{"title":"一个最勇敢的人——哭胡耀邦同志","authors":["苏金伞"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":4,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个最勇敢的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——哭胡耀邦同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏金伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“十一亿人口日”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压得人难以安静；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想不到今天一个人的死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟使十一亿人痛哭失声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说是悲痛也是愧疚："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一亿人竟不能使他活下来；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能再在会场上看到他，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能再到边远地区询问贫苦群众。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个伟人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不如一个最勇敢的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更使人尊敬："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他曾迎着冷风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推倒营筑多年的围墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放出披枷带锁的灵魂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在人们方始悟到："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与其扬手招来百万人欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不如穿上布底鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切地走进人心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１９８９年４月１５日夜"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}